snippet.title: (SM64 Hack) Shining Stars _: Another Dimensional Incident F3 REVEAL Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the secret project I'm working on! Shining Stars _: Another Dimensional Incident is a light kaizo mod continuing, and ending, the story line of SM64 Shining Stars. Star Whomp and Celestial Bowser team up to cause all kinds of alternate dimensional chaos with the 152nd Star Comet, and we must stop them!

This is a mix of SS2 Repainted, Shining Stars: The Dim Stars and Shining Stars 4!
Look forward to more previews soon!
